{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\"> EXTRACTO DE DECRETO N&#xBA; 556 EXENTO, DE 2003 </div></div>", "i": 6440471}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por decreto exento N&#xBA; 556 de fecha 18 de julio de 2003 del Ministerio de Educaci&#xF3;n, se declara para todos los efectos legales que de acuerdo a la nueva redistribuci&#xF3;n administrativa del Centro de Formaci&#xF3;n T&#xE9;cnica Iprosec, se ha modificado el Registro del nuevo domicilio de la casa central y del local seg&#xFA;n se indica:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Casa Central&nbsp;  :&nbsp;  Los Carrera N&#xBA; 418 - Osorno</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Los Carrera N&#xBA; 456 - Osorno.</div><br><div class=\"p\">Carreras&nbsp;  :&nbsp;  -&nbsp;  Administraci&#xF3;n de Empresas</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Contabilidad General</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Computacional</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Electr&#xF3;nica Industrial</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Programaci&#xF3;n Computacional</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Secretariado Ejecutivo</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Computacional</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Turismo</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Comercio Exterior</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  T&#xE9;cnico en Construcci&#xF3;n</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;  Electricidad.</div><br><br></div>", "i": 6440472}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Santiago, 6 de agosto